---

<PageLayout title={`${title} | Better Lives Building Tribes`} description="You do not feel sad exactly. You do not feel anything. Joy, excitement, sadness, anger. It is all muted or gone entirely. You go through the motions, but you feel like you are watching your life from ">
  <Section padding="lg">
    <article class="blog-post">
      <header class="blog-post__header">
        <span class="blog-post__category">{category}</span>
